ublic","site_admin":false},"parents":[{"sha":"685d5b9e930c018916e97c22cf895c90e58f950c","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vercel/next.js/commits/685d5b9e930c018916e97c22cf895c90e58f950c","html_url":"https://github.com/vercel/next.js/commit/685d5b9e930c018916e97c22cf895c90e58f950c"}]},{"sha":"685d5b9e930c018916e97c22cf895c90e58f950c","node_id":"C_kwDOBC3CitoAKDY4NWQ1YjllOTMwYzAxODkxNmU5N2MyMmNmODk1YzkwZTU4Zjk1MGM","commit":{"author":{"name":"Tim Neutkens","email":"tim@timneutkens.nl","date":"2026-05-22T15:37:23Z"},"committer":{"name":"GitHub","email":"noreply@github.com","date":"2026-05-22T15:37:23Z"},"message":"Fix pr-status job pagination (#94049)\n\n### What?\n\nLower the GitHub Actions jobs page size used by `scripts/pr-status.js`\nand keep walking pages until all jobs are fetched. Reuse the paginated\njob fetch for flaky-test detection.\n\n### Why?\n\nThe previous `per_page=100&page=1` request for run `26093602659` returns\nHTTP 502 from GitHub because the query is too slow.\n\n### How?\n\nAdd a shared `JOBS_PAGE_SIZE = 30`, update the pagination stop condition\nto match it, and route flaky-test failed job lookup through\n`getFailedJobs()`.\n\n### Verification\n\n- `node --check scripts/pr-status.js`\n- `pnpm prettier --with-node-modules --ignore-path .prettierignore\n--write scripts/pr-status.js`\n- `npx eslint --config eslint.config.mjs --fix scripts/pr-status.js`\n- `gh api\n\"repos/vercel/next.js/actions/runs/26093602659/jobs?per_page=30&page=<n>\"\n--jq \".jobs | length\"` across pages 1-5 captured 137 jobs, matching\n`total_count: 137`\n- Confirmed the old `per_page=100&page=1` request still returns HTTP 502\n- Not run: full Next.js test suite (scripts-only helper change)\n\n<!-- NEXT_JS_LLM_PR -->","tree":{"sha":"5d569b86b55f1720a62ab529b8315f8b0d966d81","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vercel/next.js/git/trees/5d569b86b55f1720a62ab529b8315f8b0d966d81"},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vercel/next.js/git/commits/685d5b9e930c018916e97c22cf895c90e58f950c","comment_count":0,"verification":{"verified":true,"reason":"valid","signature":"-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\nwsFcBAABCAAQBQJqEHgzCRC1aQ7uu5UhlAAA/+YQADEMN4K5Jx92DupbbamasRZh\nElvkzATWC9n/Y92iXtREpqdrp7I+8a6wNJgWV5HCeRA2TH0Fc0R0bCTb82DpwL8D\nMk9Umk3TJ2XToAriBidBJ/nWsJ2o4QzJPlwHb21RVE4Jm7I3jXDBrG6MMimr99J/\nyIhyY0BzFFb560B57t+igWbX8fFV8bSU6j7ZrZDfTXDmq2T8FTscW2KY/IHwcFty\n8brMCxOwW9+SQeilY7g6+8CN0dhV1m7syNnJkSZHIpiOnsWzAbh/EKkY+mzCcS+f\nzDGk1MT6xNhB0ZTDb/v3F2w4V8mczq5Jr+G0AvyyJUrdQroy4g1mL/KzO2o/fN9f\n3UGcaBzLToJsIFrcPsHOuh7jPuWwEMg1pYVyf7pb1h/YZQbZwB4k0dGxyZzMKh6H\nVnRSvSm6W89Imvdw3kU377jcm9koTT73OxO9kav4t1LRrZ3Cs1E9v4sP/WuTbluw\nHK6YJmNDH6CUR8HBkQiqK0waM3XF3x/WusZg4l7RhBCps0zEJnqMydORxNDfdQdg\n9ZaVJlDYJvVCsjEoij099VEu05mXcuZOYeuOZMaVNdETbNmKRXS/uXgUbsrw9PsG\ngdeg3cfk6xcjVGhrutas0S1ruTJlztqcVmFCOQx8Lrp4e9q/snGQglH6DDaPtjf1\n8G/AacAu4s6SWz9rRkpf\n=EMRC\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----\n","payload":"tree 5d569b86b55f1720a62ab529b8315f8b0d966d81\nparent 71036838c6e436a272e6a2ac4aedae5170a637a5\nauthor Tim Neutkens <tim@timneutkens.nl> 1779464243 +0200\ncommitter GitHub <noreply@github.com> 1779464243 +0000\n\nFix pr-status job pagination (#94049)\n\n### What?\n\nLower the GitHub Actions jobs page size used by `scripts/pr-status.js`\nand keep walking pages until all jobs are fetched. Reuse the paginated\njob fetch for flaky-test detection.\n\n### Why?\n\nThe previous `per_page=100&page=1` request for run `26093602659` returns\nHTTP 502 from GitHub because the query is too slow.\n\n### How?\n\nAdd a shared `JOBS_PAGE_SIZE = 30`, update the pagination stop condition\nto match it, and route flaky-test failed job lookup through\n`getFailedJobs()`.\n\n### Verification\n\n- `node --check scripts/pr-status.js`\n- `pnpm prettier --with-node-modules --ignore-path .prettierignore\n--write scripts/pr-status.js`\n- `npx eslint --config eslint.config.mjs --fix scripts/pr-status.js`\n- `gh api\n\"repos/vercel/next.js/actions/runs/26093602659/jobs?per_page=30&page=<n>\"\n--jq \".jobs | length\"` across pages 1-5 captured 137 jobs, matching\n`total_count: 137`\n- Confirmed the old `per_page=100&page=1` request still returns HTTP 502\n- Not run: full Next.js test suite (scripts-only helper change)\n\n<!-- NEXT_JS_LLM_PR -->","verified_at":"2026-05-22T15:37:23Z"}},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vercel/next.js/commits/685d5b9e930c018916e97c22cf895c90e58f950c","html_url":"https://github.com/vercel/next.js/commit/685d5b9e930c018916e97c22cf895c90e58f950c","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vercel/next.js/commits/685d5b9e930c018916e97c22cf895c90e58f950c/comments","author":{"login":"timneutkens","id":6324199,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjYzMjQxOTk=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6324199?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/timneutkens","html_url":"https://github.com/timneutkens","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timneutkens/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timneutkens/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timneutkens/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timneutkens/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timneutkens/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timneutkens/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timneutkens/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timneutkens/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timneutkens/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"committer":{"login":"web-flow","id":19864447,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE5ODY0NDQ3","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19864447?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow","html_url":"https://github.com/web-flow","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://ap